# Design Decisions

## Reservations

- Customers pay the entire purchase amount.
- One purchase may contain multiple seats.
- Each seat checks in separately.
- Hold seats do not count as revenue.
- Paid seats count toward revenue.

## Events

- Data is stored locally.
- Events are archived permanently.
- Ticket prices are configurable for each event.
- Presale and Day-of prices are tracked separately.

## Design

- Large touch-friendly buttons.
- Designed primarily for iPad.
- Must work offline.
